<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forgot Password - Taco Joes Rewards</title>
    <link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        img {
        width: 220px;
        }

        .email-container {
        background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);
        height: auto;
        width: 100%;
        border: 2px solid #000000;
        text-align: center;
        }

        .password-container {
        width: 180px;
        background-color: #cce2c4;
        margin: auto;
        margin-top: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 0px;
        }

        h1 {
        color: #789c59;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        font-size: 22px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0px;
        }

        h1.orange {
        color: #da913f;
        }

        p {
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding-left: 10px;
        padding-right: 10px;

        }

        p.bold {
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
        }
    </style>
    <div class="email-container">
        <img src="tacoJoesImage.jpg">

        <h1 class="orange">Recover Your Account</h1>

        <p>You recently requested to reset your Taco Joes Rewards password. Use the temporary password provided below to log in to your account.</p>
            
        <p>Once logged in, please change your password. This temporary password will no longer be available after logging in.</p>
        
        <p class="bold">Temporary Password:</p>
        <div class="password-container">
            <h1><%= mailOptionsAdditions.password %></h1>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    
    
</body>
</html>